    "source_id": "tae-kim-grammar",
    "source_key": "tae-kim:imperative-form",
    "slug": "imperative-form",
    "category": "commands",
    "list_name": "requests-and-commands",
    "expression": "命令形",
    "connection": "一段动词去る + ろ；五段动词末音变为え段；する→しろ，来る→こい；否定为辞书形 + な",
    "explanation_zh": "用强硬语气直接命令对方行动，日常会话中适用范围很有限。",
    "source_url": "https://www.guidetojapanese.org/requests.html",
    "license_key": "cc-by-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-14",
    "display_order": 56,
    "published": true,
    "path": "core",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "危ない、止まれ！",
        "zh": "危险，停下！",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "命令形语气很强，不是普通的“请”；对不熟悉的人应优先使用「～てください」等合适请求形式。"
